        <mxCell id="5wku5PaAa4V_MW-_MLWo-72" parent="vOXxB0WhoqEsLinS-9xs-3" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=15;fontColor=default;labelBackgroundColor=light-dark(#f8f8f8, #ededed);textShadow=0;strokeColor=light-dark(#e2e2e2, #ededed);shadow=0;" value="&lt;p class=&quot;mb-2 last:mb-0&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.92 0.004 286.32); margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;Сервер маркировки не хранит конфигурацию объектов. Топология (цеха, автоматы, сотрудники, назначения) вынесена в отдельную БД с доступом по REST API и кешированием по ETag.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;mb-2 last:mb-0&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.92 0.004 286.32); margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.92 0.004 286.32); margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;Мобильный монитор:&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;list-disc list-outside pl-5 mb-2 space-y-1&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.92 0.004 286.32); margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; list-style: outside disc; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.92 0.004 286.32); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; --tw-space-y-reverse: 0; margin-block: 0px 4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.92 0.004 286.32); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.92 0.004 286.32); margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;Аутентификация&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.92 0.004 286.32); margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;—&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bg-muted px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-[11px]&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; border-radius: 0.25rem; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.92 0.004 286.32); margin: 0px; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; padding-inline: 4px; padding-block: 2px;&quot;&